"ht "
"(vergelijkbaar met het 003 Cokin(tm) Red filter)."

#: ../../image_editor/colors_tools.rst:104
msgid ""
"**Yellow Filter**: simulates black & white film exposure with yellow lens "
"filter. Provides most natural tonal correction, and improves contrast. Ide"
"al "
